# Spec and Task Workflow

- Work strictly phase-by-phase: `task1.md` -> `task2.md` -> ... -> `task9.md`.
- Do not jump to the next task file before finishing the current one.
- Keep `SPEC.md` progress fields aligned with real task state.
- Update "next session note" sections when pausing or finishing a step.
- Prefer small, verifiable changes and mark checklist items immediately.
- Keep requirements in markdown authoritative; avoid hidden assumptions in chat-only context.
